# Project rules for aod-tpw-from-radiation

- Use Anaconda Python at `/opt/anaconda3/bin/python` (or `PATH` with `/opt/anaconda3/bin` first) when running project scripts from the terminal.
- Refer to `.agents/SKILL.md` for coding standards.
- Maintain numbered scripts (1.arrange, 2.create_holdout, etc.).
- Ensure `libRadtran.py` remains a pure library without side effects on import.
